-- Janus’s Chairman Scheid to Retire in April, Replaced by Schafer
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   C o n d o n
-- 2012-01-26T14:22:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-26/janus-s-chairman-scheid-to-retire-in-april-replaced-by-schafer.html
Steven L. Scheid, chairman of
Denver-based Janus Capital Group Inc., will retire at the end of
April after leading the company’s board of directors for eight
years.  Glenn S. Schafer, a director since December 2007, will
replace Scheid as chairman, the company said today in a
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christopher Condon in Boston at 
 ccondon4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
